(change / 2) * Math.pow(t, 3) : (change / 2) * (Math.pow(t - 2, 3) + 2)); carousel.style.top = top + "px"; }, 1000 / 60); } function setupCarousel(containerId, carouselId, downButtonId, upButtonId) { var container = document.getElementById(containerId); var carousel = document.getElementById(carouselId); var downButton = document.getElementById(downButtonId); var upButton = document.getElementById(upButtonId); downButton.onclick = function () { rotateForward(carousel); animate( carousel, -Carousel.rowHeight * Carousel.visibleRows, 0, function () {} ); }; upButton.onclick = function () { animate( carousel, 0, -Carousel.rowHeight * Carousel.visibleRows, function () { rotateBackward(carousel); carousel.style.top = "0"; } ); }; } window.onload = function () { setupCarousel("containerActor", "carouselActor", "downActor", "upActor"); setupCarousel( "containerDirector", "carouselDirector", "downDirector", "upDirector" ); setupCarousel( "containerSource", "carouselSource", "downSource", "upSource" ); setupCarousel( "containerScenario", "carouselScenario", "downScenario", "upScenario" ); setupCarousel("containerAdapt", "carouselAdapt", "downAdapt", "upAdapt"); }; return (
